➜北京双星伴月形似“歪嘴笑脸”，萌翻了！网友调侃：一眼大一眼小
http://www.sohu.com/a/433050293_255783	5190
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201120/12f31068ae124de38a738bb877df7b1f.png" /></p>
<p><strong>网友评论</strong></p>
<p>网友：哇，好美啊</p>
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201120/774072350ea147fa80751f83350bcdc5.png" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201120/26652ae9481048a1a91f2c1f7bd96b24.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
