➜痛心！女童误服近40粒降压药后不幸身亡，医生紧急提醒
http://www.sohu.com/a/433052001_255783	5473
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201120/4a50c82c667b4e2b801c9df424a2bcbc.png" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201120/b5ef9b91fd3d4e30a534b77048787f8c.png" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201120/1a82330b10934ea99e3b3a01194c3c39.png" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201120/5d29d70389b5410aacc4430b60025642.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
